data.description: Country Living at it's best. This charming house is the perfect place for entertaining, the kitchen is the perfect size to host those holiday gatherings with enough room in the attached dining room to all sit together. The main floor also could be used for a bedroom or office and has a full bath and laundry area. The upstairs has 4 bedrooms along with original hardwoods throughout. A detached garage/barn/work space is an added plus.  Don't miss out, come see for yourself!
